To create an integration between Twilio's Video JavaScript SDK and AWS Streaming Transcription Service, we will write a basic code outline that demonstrates the key steps for setting up and establishing a connection between both services.

This example assumes that you have already set up your AWS account and added the necessary credentials on your server.

First, include the needed libraries:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
