<p>The variable "query" holds the name we are looking for, and we set the "found" flag to false at the beginning. We then loop through each element of the array until we find a match, setting the "found" flag to true if we do. We return the value of "found" to indicate whether the name was found or not.</p>

<p>To delete a name from the array, you can simply remove it from the variable where it is stored.</p>
